title: TWELVE YEARS LATER / Geronimo Pratt
description:
For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub

TWELVE YEARS LATER / Geronimo Pratt | interviewed by Sylvester Rivers.

Former Black Panther, Geronimo Pratt, imprisoned on a murder charge despite much contrary evidence, discusses his service in the Vietnam War, his experiences in prison, the Black Panthers being targeted by COINTELPRO, and the infiltration of his defense proceedings by the FBI.

RECORDED: San Quentin prison, Calif., 27 Nov. 1981. 

BROADCAST: KPFK, 14 Dec. 1981
